entries.femaleVariant: Preem work, V! Seriously, mad respect. Closin' the gig and sendin' the eds.
You persuaded Mausser...?! Fuckin' hell, if I knew you could wag your tongue like that I coulda made you NC's richest drink-slinger. Wastin' your talents on the street 'stead of behind a bar.
Heard whispers Mausser bit the concrete. Nicely done.
Gig's sealed – and your boy Dino needs a drink. Later, V.
But cool, cool – if Mausser's gone, so's the problem. You get your eddies, I close the gig. All good? All good.
Supposed to end Mausser, not just give him a headache. Sorry, no cred for that move.
